label.mutableString:
The Holo App is an app developed to enable people with speaking challenges easily communicate with others. The idea was born while playing with my cousin who is on the Autism Spectrum. He is non verbal, but can point to text and read well.
I hope this app will help him. However, my bigger goal is to see if this idea can help other children and adults who are facing this challenge in communicating with the world. This is a totally free app.
I look forward to your ideas, suggestions and comments. Please do write to me at isojassethi@icloud.com
